name: Gungan Guard
Lore: 'Equipped with portable Gungan shields, these front line troops provide a secondary defense against blaster fire.',
Text: 'Your Gungan leaders present may not be targeted by weapons. While defending a battle on Naboo, Power +4 and, whenever you draw a Gungan for battle destiny, add 3 to that destiny. Requires +2 Force to use landspeed.',
